description: Smash Time Food Truck has crashed onto the Cleveland streets with its delicious selection of comfort cuisine.Their insanely tasty menu may continually change but a few of the mouthwatering items you’ll find include…The Kevin Mack-N-Cheese (with ooey gooey gouda, bacon & scallions), The Halle Berry Taco (with honey-garlic pork, sweet peppers, lettuce, strawberry salsa, greek yogurt & white cheddar cheese), Open Faced Pulled Pork “Smashwich” (densely scrumptious cornbread topped with juicy BBQ pulled pork, pickled red onions, and slaw), and so much more. Mmmm...are you feeling like it might be time to eat? Well, come on to this truck soon or invite it to your next event and smash the appetites of all your guests with all this awesome food!
name: Smash Time Food Truck
